The paper proposes a novel method to learn a neural program to operate a non-differentiable machine, which involves reinforcement learning-based search techniques. This work involves machine learning, artificial intelligence, and programming languages, which are all relevant to the sub-categories of cs.AI, cs.LG, and cs.PL.
